<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>럭셔리 리조트 & 스파</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #d4af37;
        }
        
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1920x1080.png?text=Luxury+Resort+View');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .hero-content {
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.6);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        main {
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .feature {
            flex: 1;
            margin: 0 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   {{>layouts/header}}
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>럭셔리 리조트 & 스파</h1>
            <p>최고의 휴식과 힐링을 경험하세요</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main>
        <h2>리조트 특징</h2>
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200.png?text=Luxury+Room" alt="고급 객실">
                <h3>최고급 객실</h3>
                <p>편안함과 럭셔리함이 공존하는 객실</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200.png?text=Spa" alt="스파">
                <h3>힐링 스파</h3>
                <p>몸과 마음의 휴식을 위한 프리미엄 스파</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200.png?text=Gourmet+Dining" alt="고급 다이닝">
                <h3>미식 다이닝</h3>
                <p>최고의 셰프가 선보이는 특별한 요리</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>